Big Brother Naija Housemate, Kiddwaya has said that he feels that he has achieved a lot just by being in the lockdown house. Kiddwaya, during a conversation with Laycon on Thursday morning said he feels like he has achieved a lot because he has spent up to 8 weeks in the house. He also said that whether he gets evicted on Sunday or not, he will still be grateful, as staying in the house for this long is already an achievement. “If I make it past the Sunday eviction or not, either way, I will be okay. “There are so much to be thankful for and I will be equally grateful that I got this far. “I keep telling everyone that whether you stay till the end, you have to be proud of yourself for coming this far. “ I feel like I have achieved a lot just by being in this house and staying this long,” he said.